<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4608129>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 7. Dicerapanorpa kimminsi, genitalia, from Mt Emei, Sichuan. (A, B) Genital bulb of male, dorsal and ventral views; (C) same, ventral view with hypovalves removed; (D) aedeagus complex, ventral view; (E) abdominal segments IX–XI of female, ventral view; (F) subgenital plate, ventral view; (G–I) genital plate, ventral, lateral and dorsal views. Scale bars: A–C, E, F = 0.5 mm; D, G–I = 0.2 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4608129/files/figure.png" .

