        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 6. Dicerapanorpa kimminsi, from Mt Emei, Sichuan. (A) Male, dorsal view; (B) female, dorsal view; (C) head of male, frontal view; (D) abdominal segments V–XI of male, lateral view; (E) tergum VI of male, dorsal view, showing anal horns. Scale bars: A and B = 3.0 mm; C and E = 0.5 mm; D = 1.0 mm." ;
